Method Detail

run

public OptInfo run(DepotLinkedList mainDepots)
Attempts to use a smaller truck in place of this truck. Chooses a truck that is of any size, but the smallest for that customer type and creates a truck with the next smallest size. As many customers as possible are placed into the smaller truck and the rest are inserted into the other trucks in the solution. The changes will be kept if the new configuration yields a better cost than before. The attemptToRelocateTruck() is called to check the possibility.
